{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0397726cbb","title":"在一份介绍老子哲学是唯物主义还是唯心主义的争论材料上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0df9de9bc3","index":0,"year":1959,"month":12,"day":27,"articleId":"0397726cbb"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji42","name":"毛泽东全集第42卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/42-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji42":{"comments":[{"id":"5e2eb5bc2b","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"0397726cbb","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这份材料介绍说，在认为老子哲学基本上是唯物主义的人当中，些人认为老子的自然观是唯物的，未涉及老子的认识论；另一些人认为老子的自然观和认识论都基本上是唯物的。而认为老子哲学基本上是唯心主义的人，则认为老子的自然观和认识论都是唯心的。上述双方从老子书中引证的话，一部分是相同的，但所作的解释客不相同：另一部分引文则客不相同。这篇材料还列举了《老子》一书中的十五段引文，分别介绍了持两种观点的人对这些引文所作的不同解释。"},{"id":"a3fc2e2cf2","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"0397726cbb","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"高智，当时任毛泽东办公室秘书。"}],"contents":[{"id":"9f453a4d77","type":"title","text":"在一份介绍老子哲学是唯物主义还是唯心主义的争论材料叫上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"0397726cbb"},{"id":"5e2eb5bc2b","type":"paragraph","text":"印10份，交我为盼。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"0397726cbb"},{"id":"a3fc2e2cf2","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"0397726cbb"},{"id":"b69b8ea982","type":"paragraph","text":"廿七日上午六时","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"0397726cbb"},{"id":"ae557ebe0a","type":"subtitle","text":"高智办。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"0397726cbb"}],"page":{"id":"1ef48c19f1","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"0397726cbb","start":533,"end":533}}}},"__N_SSG":true}